<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Billionaire Justin Hemmes, 48, is dating model Madeline Holtnazgel, 24, more than two years after confirming his split from designer, Kate Fowler.</p>

<p>And according to The Daily Telegraph on Saturday, the pub baron's new girlfriend has 'moved into his beachfront apartment in Sydney's Coogee'.</p>

<p>The publication understands Justin purchased the three-bedroom property six years ago for $2.1million.</p>

<p>Love nest? According to The Daily Telegraph on Saturday, model Madeline Holtznagel (pictured), 24, has 'moved into' billionaire boyfriend Justin Hemmes' $2.1million beachfront apartment in Sydney's Coogee </p>

<p>It is also believed the father-of-two resides in his family's Vaucluse mansion, visiting Madeline at the Coogee abode.</p>

<p>Daily Mail Australia has reached out to Justin Hemmes for comment. </p>

<p>Justin was spotted aboard his luxury jet Bombardier Challenger last Saturday, celebrating his birthday week with Madeline and several of their friends. </p>

<p>When asked about his new romance with the youthful stunner, a coy Justin told The Daily Telegraph: 'We hang out a bit.' </p>

